description: We offer full weekend rentals for weddings. We believe this provides the best option to allow you to have the rehearsal, rehearsal dinner, and decorating on Friday, the wedding on Saturday, and cleanup on Sunday. Our current cost for 2026 weddings is $6,500.00 for the weekend which will begin from Friday at 9:00am through Sunday at 12:00pm. Sales tax will be added to all rentals. Luckily, all we require to reserve your requested date is a $1,000.00 deposit that is deducted from the total cost of the venue. We take cash, checks, debit and credit cards - Visa, Mastercard, Discover, or American Express. All balances must be paid in full 60 days before your event, however, we allow you to make payments at any time for however much you desire! Once you book, we allow you to use the facility for engagement pictures or bridal portraits.  The following amenities are included in the barn rental listed by the area they are located:  Chapel:  Stained Glass Windows  LED Candles  Dimmed Lighting Capacity: 180 guests seated for ceremony.
